ARTMOD - The ultimate car modification directory for the automotive industry in the Nigeria

Exterior Styling, Detailing, Performance, Wrapping & much more! Use our website to find an automotive product or service near you.

ARTMOD was created by a car enthusiasts who experienced the same difficulty finding the right suppliers for both parts and fitting for the perfect modification. The result is a mutually beneficial online directory, where car enthusiasts and automotive suppliers can co-exist. As the central hub for the automotive industry, we provide a platform for suppliers to promote their products and services to car enthusiasts. Mod Central brings both areas into one website and makes the process smoother for both customer and supplier.
